OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1777172626
OL,3,CMan extradited from the UAE to appear
OL,4,Cin court charged with woman's murder
OL,6,FPolice successfully extradited 18-year-
OL,7,Fold Bettamio, of no fixed address, on
OL,8,Fa flight from Dubai to the UK on
OL,9,FFriday following joint enquiries by
OL,10,Fthe Metropolitan Police and specialist
OL,11,Flawyers in the Crown Prosecution
OL,12,FService's extradition and
OL,13,Finternational units.
OL,15,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,16,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,17,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,18,Finbox every Friday morning.
