OL,3,CMan extradited from the UAE to appear
OL,4,Cin court charged with woman's murder
OL,6,FMs Thiamphanit was found by police at
OL,7,Fher home in Stanhope Place, Bayswater,
OL,8,Fat around 8.30am on Monday, April 8,
OL,9,F2024 with multiple stab wounds. She
OL,10,Fwas pronounced dead at the scene.
OL,12,FBettamio will appear at Westminster
OL,13,FMagistrates' Court on Saturday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/5
