PN,31304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1777172626
OL,3,CMan extradited from the UAE to appear
OL,4,Cin court charged with woman's murder
OL,6,FDetective chief inspector Alison
OL,7,FFoxwell, who is leading the
OL,8,Finvestigation, said: "I would also
OL,9,Flike to express my sincere thanks to
OL,10,FAngela's family and friends for their
OL,11,Fpatience and unwavering support to the
OL,12,Finvestigation, throughout what has
OL,13,Fbeen an incredibly difficult and
OL,14,Fdistressing time for them."
OL,16,FThe Met had referred itself to the
OL,17,FIndependent Office for Police Conduct
OL,18,Ffollowing the murder, after officers
OL,19,Fwere contacted twice by friends of Ms
OL,20,FThiamphanit the day before her body
OL,21,Fwas discovered.
