OL,3,CMan extradited from the UAE to appear
OL,4,Cin court charged with woman's murder
OL,6,FThe case was graded as a medium-risk
OL,7,Fmissing person inquiry before officers
OL,8,Fforced entry and discovered the 27-
OL,9,Fyear-old, who had Chinese, Hong Kong
OL,10,Fand Thai nationality.
OL,12,FHave you heard our podcast Talking
